    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are a wandering ninja, a shinobi not attached to any village either from being a missing-nin or from being raised or trained by one, or another wandering ninja.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Wandering Ninja.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Core</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 15+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Climb, Chakra Control, Craft (calligraphy), Disable Device, Escape Artist, Fuinjutsu, Gamble, Genjutsu, Knowledge (current events), Knowledge (ninja lore), Knowledge (tactics), Listen, Ninjutsu, Perform, Sleight of Hand, Survival, Swim, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Archaic Weapon Proficiency, Brawl, Combat Martial Arts, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Precise Shot.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +2</p>"
